{"tid":1696931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議:和你放工,為罷工集氣!!","createTime":"2019-11-06T13:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T15:43:07.000Z","uid":95299,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6468defffe4a4aefecb0fa02e69db0021e0e0c99","tid":1696931,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"如果可以係放工時間5區快閃，可能有以下優點<br />\n<br />\n1.塞車(警車,水炮車入唔到, 如果黨鐵放工時唔郁就仲大鑊了)<br />\n2.成街都係人，不能tg/亂拉人<br />\n3.冇人閙阻返工 <br />\n4.知道有冇同事參與，準備罷工(小心督灰)<br />\n5.如公司提早放工, 可以提早快閃，loop到罷工，循序漸進，罷工更易入口<br />\n6.和平狀態下放tg/亂拉人都唔錯<br />\n7.容易集中起office區，影響好多公司，有tg就仲正<br />\n8.港豬燒到埋身(示威日終於多過平日，仲要冇得避，應該唔會輸民意掛...)<br />\n9.加強假宵禁/逼政府真宵禁<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗?"},{"pid":"e6e76f5296e24e48df54f450574177a15c151a15","tid":1696931,"uid":118564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4bb94f5521b0f76c93dc71fbd73e4665b1f7851","tid":1696931,"uid":41736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"9b1115c306cff0a7f12cf5b35fb4435c3a3f9780","tid":1696931,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"psih"},{"pid":"ed848cced57090aa7e7d19fde7a9c55118ac6eb7","tid":1696931,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f8d4bfdeef3619189a396466866848deb8fad1","tid":1696931,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:40:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696924\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696924</a>"},{"pid":"a42da6e44e5158d0503e135dd711fd92dc741a6d","tid":1696931,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"Office區暫時都係春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c45728905fcb16090a044f3ac31b764e64c3c86","tid":1696931,"uid":329453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"如果係要落到商業區,其實唔使咁複雜,嘥尻氣叫心罷工啦,商業區放工前集合流水式遊行,不裝修,確保好退路,有狗來就且戰且退, d返工既, 公司既, 硬食狗逗, 封路, 就會發爛渣,適當時候,出返來幫手保護,開路,幫佢地離開,急救, 贏民意啦"},{"pid":"a42586d2581419b457cee7f09f67995819db9a04","tid":1696931,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c45728905fcb16090a044f3ac31b764e64c3c86","tid":1696931,"uid":329453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"如果係要落到商業區,其實唔使咁複雜,嘥尻氣叫心罷工啦,商業區放工前集合流水式遊行,不裝修,確保好退路,有狗來就且戰且退, d返工既, 公司既, 硬食狗逗, 封路, 就會發爛渣,適當時候,出返來幫手保護,開路,幫佢地離開,急救, 贏民意啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d84319072cf24b8d6df7dd776d320092ecafbc","tid":1696931,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"自推01/10"},{"pid":"26529ae814fc083d1a7b73f84a5f78671d0e9be9","tid":1696931,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"幫下呢位手足 由6月努力到而家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a36140fe2ab67b5e0ada34ccd37ded4ec99177d","tid":1696931,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"自推02/10"},{"pid":"2ed9a3c549e793ffbf3be013c0b306654a5e0b6c","tid":1696931,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"自推03/10"},{"pid":"040d6dac014c19a6627d603a9a4c5e997ac2d9f2","tid":1696931,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n阻返工一定好過阻放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9d3e2f504af996438e27c736f34203e8dc2e59","tid":1696931,"uid":95299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"自推04/10 呢個係慢慢集人氣,然後去罷工<br />\n依家D人就係驚自己一條友罷, 因為依家感受唔到果種氣氛"